Device and Activity Monitoring Technologies
We use technologies such as session replay tools that monitor, and may record, your interactions with the Service and Digital Properties, including without limitation, keystrokes and how you move through and engage with the Service and Digital Properties. These technologies may also collect and analyze information from your Device, such as, without limitation, your operating system, plug-ins, system fonts, and other data.

Purposes for using these technologies. We and authorized third parties use these Tracking Technologies for purposes including:

Personalization, such as remembering user preferences, login details and browsing behavior; tracking your activity across online properties and platforms over time to better understand your preferences and interests; and personalizing online content;
Improving performance, such as maintaining and improving the performance of the Service and Digital Properties;
Analytics, such as analyzing how the Service and Digital Properties are used to help us improve the Service’s and Digital Properties’ performance and user experience;
Advertising, such as providing you with offers that may be of interest to you; conducting targeted advertising to you on the Service and Digital Properties, as well as digital properties of third parties; and measuring the effectiveness of our communications with you and advertising campaigns, including identifying how and when you engage with our communications; and
Security, such as user or Device identification and prevention of fraud and malicious behavior.

